{"tid":1829680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆 人肉口循化","createTime":"2020-01-19T03:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T04:09:06.000Z","uid":37959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb643d275bf67e04cfcd02745eb32438137f074","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"日日咁貼 日日咁撕 都唔係辦法<br />\n港豬冇人日日提住 係唔識嬲 唔識反抗<br />\n場運動就凍哂 完埋<br />\n<br />\n建議：全面恢復10點鐘鳩嗌<br />\n<br />\n建議二：每個鐘鳩嗌<br />\n不論係屋企/係街都要咁做<br />\n鳩嗌內容係任何連儂牆會出現既資訊<br />\n<br />\n而家條街咁多人帶口罩 邊個會知係你嗌？<br />\n遊行集會就好威威咁大大聲叫 又唱肥媽又盛<br />\n叫你一個帶住口罩係條街鳩嗌就唔敢<br />\n如果因為怕柒 怕比人笑 怕比人當癲佬而唔做<br />\n咁香港變左新疆就唔好怪人<br />\n<br />\n利申：日日放工會嗌 好舒暢"},{"pid":"431377c869c4cef2e6188d5ec5a38b796767a89c","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c7509d7733a3cd26a15aa820237e470f5590a38a","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cac038c4af95419623d542ddad93d7e910ed90c3","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5a01ca016deca61505c2f667c58ab0328862fec0","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8bf6faa19b86710e815a772b0bb5c09ae9b552a1","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a031cb5e22d9fa29004cc898cc8e429858c58fff","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ec8a6bcd29ab9ee8b4b9db2411ddb672bbf018a3","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"36c72382b41279142c241f204673bd42f4f53cdc","tid":1829680,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"